{"word":"G3115 - μακροθυμία - makrothymía - mak-roth-oo-mee'-ah - Longsuffering","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μακροθυμία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>makrothymía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mak-roth-oo-mee'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Longsuffering"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நீடிய சாந்தம், நீடிய பொறுமை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. patience, endurance, constancy, steadfastness, perseverance"},{"paragraph":"2. forbearance, long - suffering, slowness in avenging wrongs"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the same as <a href=\"#/G3116 - μακροθυμώς - makrothymṓs - mak-roth-oo-moce'/3116\">G3116</a>; <i>longanimity</i>, that is, (objectively) <i>forbearance</i> or (subjectively) <i>fortitude:</i> - longsuffering, patience."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3114 - μακροθυμέω - makrothyméō - mak-roth-oo-meh'-o/3114\">G3114</a>, <a href=\"#/G3115 - μακροθυμία - makrothymía - mak-roth-oo-mee'-ah/3115\">G3115</a>, <a href=\"#/G3116 - μακροθυμώς - makrothymṓs - mak-roth-oo-moce'/3116\">G3116</a>"}]}